---
import ArrowRightIcon from '@/components/icons/ArrowRight.astro'
---
<section class="flex justify-center items-center">
  <div class="flex flex-col justify-center items-center gap-5">
    <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-6xl lg:text-7xl text-center">
      <span class="text-primary">Crea tu propia</span>
      <br />
      <span class="text-primary opacity-70">TierList aqu√≠</span>
    </h2>

    <p class="text-lg text-pretty text-center px-3 sm:px-4 md:px-0">
      Si prefieres, puedes usar alguna de las TierList que ya han sido creadas por la comunidad.
    </p>

    <aside class="flex justify-center items-center gap-4">
      <button
        class="inline-flex group items-center justify-center gap-3 rounded-md text-sm font-bold ring-offset-background transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 bg-primary text-primary-foreground hover:bg-slate-100/90 h-10 px-4 py-2"
      >
        <span class="text-black/80"> Crear TierList </span>
        <ArrowRightIcon class="size-6 text-black group-hover:-rotate-45 transition duration-300" />
      </button>

      <a
        href="https://github.com/MartL7"
        aria-label="Ir al Github del Creador"
        class="inline-flex group items-center justify-center gap-3 rounded-md text-sm font-bold ring-offset-background transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 bg-primary text-primary-foreground hover:bg-slate-100/90 h-10 px-4 py-2"
      >
        <span class="text-black/80"> Ir al Github </span>
        <ArrowRightIcon class="size-6 text-black group-hover:-rotate-45 transition duration-300" />
      </a>
    </aside>
  </div>
</section>
